    "endTime": 6.673,
    "text": "Squidward!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.549,
    "endTime": 8.675,
    "text": "Well, he's not here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.759,
    "endTime": 11.97,
    "text": "I bet that eager beaver is\nalready down at Jellyfish Fields."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.804,
    "endTime": 15.224,
    "text": "Ah-ha! They've finally gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.892,
    "endTime": 19.645,
    "text": "What the--\nLocked? Oh, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.229,
    "endTime": 24.107,
    "text": "Well, someone will realize I'm gone\nand come looking for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.191,
    "endTime": 26.985,
    "text": "I'll be out of here in no time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.795,
    "endTime": 46.547000000000004,
    "text": "Holy Krabby Patties!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.63,
    "endTime": 48.507000000000005,
    "text": "A frozen cephalopod!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.722,
    "endTime": 56.849000000000004,
    "text": "[screaming]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.225,
    "endTime": 60.519,
    "text": "I'll be out of here in no time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.561,
    "endTime": 61.687,
    "text": "Greetings, primitive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.02,
    "endTime": 63.772000000000006,
    "text": "Sp-- SpongeBob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.814,
    "endTime": 65.065,
    "text": "Is that you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.44,
    "endTime": 66.567,
    "text": "SpongeBob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.775,
    "endTime": 69.278,
    "text": "No, I am SpongeTron."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.611,
    "endTime": 70.90400000000001,
    "text": "Welcome to the future."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.655,
    "endTime": 73.74,
    "text": "- What?\n- Welcome to the future."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.246,
    "endTime": 81.832,
    "text": "Future!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.252,
    "endTime": 86.92,
    "text": "Holy sea cow, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.129,
    "endTime": 89.548,
    "text": "This must be the control room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.382,
    "endTime": 92.551,
    "text": "Yeah, just don't touch anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.718,
    "endTime": 94.13600000000001,
    "text": "Look, I'm winning!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.845,
    "endTime": 96.346,
    "text": "Patrick, cut that out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.889,
    "endTime": 98.223,
    "text": "Patrick, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.307,
    "endTime": 99.72500000000001,
    "text": "We can't hang around in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.808,
    "endTime": 103.77000000000001,
    "text": "This is Sandy's big rocket,\nnot some kind of fun... house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.98,
    "endTime": 108.4,
    "text": "Woohoo, winner!\nYeah, high score!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.609,
    "endTime": 110.56899999999999,
    "text": "Say Patrick, what game was that anyway?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.819,
    "endTime": 113.071,
    "text": "I don't know,\nbut let's see what this does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.155,
    "endTime": 114.44800000000001,
    "text": "Patrick, I don't think we should--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.866,
    "endTime": 116.992,
    "text": "I like rockets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.284,
    "endTime": 118.45200000000001,
    "text": "[yelling]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.578,
    "endTime": 120.87100000000001,
    "text": "More! More!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.246,
    "endTime": 122.33099999999999,
    "text": "No more!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.456,
    "endTime": 123.62400000000001,
    "text": "[yelling]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.004,
    "endTime": 130.339,
    "text": "OK, one more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.464,
    "endTime": 131.548,
    "text": "[yelling]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.052,
    "endTime": 137.012,
    "text": "- OK, that's enough, let's go.\n- Wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.137,
    "endTime": 140.265,
    "text": "- I think this one starts it--\n- Patrick, what are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.307,
    "endTime": 141.975,
    "text": "I'm the space traveler here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.017,
    "endTime": 144.64499999999998,
    "text": "And I happen to know\nthat that particular button is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.728,
    "endTime": 146.23000000000002,
    "text": "right over here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.313,
    "endTime": 147.606,
    "text": "[engine roaring]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.273,
    "endTime": 149.816,
    "text": "You started the rocket!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.319,
    "endTime": 155.03,
    "text": "Oh... SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.282,
    "endTime": 158.40800000000002,
    "text": "[screaming]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.082,
    "endTime": 166.25,
    "text": "Hang on, buddy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.333,
    "endTime": 167.334,
    "text": "[screaming]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.838,
    "endTime": 172.673,
    "text": "Hey, we stopped falling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.006,
    "endTime": 175.133,
    "text": "Look, we're in space now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.259,
    "endTime": 176.635,
    "text": "Wee!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.01,
    "endTime": 178.053,
    "text": "[moaning]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.596,
    "endTime": 183.892,
    "text": "Hey, somebody get me down,\nor up or something!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.934,
    "endTime": 184.935,
    "text": "[laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.145,
    "endTime": 189.14700000000002,
    "text": "Ha, hey SpongeBob, watch this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.731,
    "endTime": 193.10999999999999,
    "text": "Hey! You got your tooth paste\nin my peanut butter!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.443,
    "endTime": 194.48600000000002,
    "text": "[laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.405,
    "endTime": 198.74,
    "text": "Uh-oh, we've got space junk!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.824,
    "endTime": 201.869,
    "text": "Everybody, back in your seats.\nTrays in upright position."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.952,
    "endTime": 204.913,
    "text": "Head between your knees.\nYour mama can't save you now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.038,
    "endTime": 206.20600000000002,
    "text": "[moaning]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.751,
    "endTime": 210.919,
    "text": "[alarm ringing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.337,
    "endTime": 214.089,
    "text": "Hi-ya!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.381,
    "endTime": 215.632,
    "text": "[cheering]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.848,
    "endTime": 225.01700000000002,
    "text": "We've still got a few\nastro-belts to get through."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.142,
    "endTime": 227.394,
    "text": "Brace yourself for the cold belt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.441,
    "endTime": 233.692,
    "text": "[teeth chattering]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.613,
    "endTime": 238.864,
    "text": "[humming]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.866,
    "endTime": 242.07500000000002,
    "text": "[laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.746,
    "endTime": 247.87300000000002,
    "text": "Next up, we got a hot belt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.846,
    "endTime": 263.931,
    "text": "Patty melt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.141,
    "endTime": 269.144,
    "text": "Huh? We're going through\nthe radiation belt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.228,
    "endTime": 272.523,
    "text": "That could cause mutations!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.564,
    "endTime": 274.942,
    "text": "Everybody, get under your lead blankets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.567,
    "endTime": 279.112,
    "text": "Mutations? I must protect\nmy beautiful face!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.378,
    "endTime": 295.587,
    "text": "[laughing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.173,
    "endTime": 299.174,
    "text": "Aw."
  }
]